imdb.plot outline: Ilmar Molder is Vennori in this high adrenaline and painful-to-watch comedy gaming series where he plays incredibly difficult and popular video games while wearing a shock collar, normally intended for dogs, around his neck. Every time Vennori swears, dies, fails, or cant complete a challenge he must shock himself with the shock collar, and increase the pain level of the collar by a certain amount. Special guests appear in the series as "Electro-cutioners" who do the shocking for Vennori, as they cringe and be thankful it isn't them with the collar around their necks.
imdb.title: Shock Collar Kingdom
plot: Vennori plays the most difficult video games in the world while wearing a shock collar around his neck, trying to complete challenges and finish the game without getting shocked.::Vennori
